Package: planisphere
Title: Map projections
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Nicolas",
                    family = "Lambert",
                    email = "nicolas.lambert@cnrs.fr", 
                    role = c("aut", "cre"),
                    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4976-6560")))
Description: Applies cartographic projections to spatial data frames containing
    geographic coordinates. Projection methods are based on the D3.js ecosystem
    <doi:10.1109/TVCG.2011.185> and use spherical geometry rather than
    ellipsoidal geodesic models. 
License: GPL (>= 3)
